# DO commit the rendered hero video so static deploys (GitHub Pages,
# Railway static) work without running Remotion. Remove these two lines
# if you'd rather render in CI on every deploy.
!remotion-hero/out/
!remotion-hero/out/*.mp4
!remotion-hero/out/*.webm
